      },
      "date": "2013-07-04 19:28:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/79e16a9c-e4de-11e2-9f63-52540035b04c).  Ran 15 tests.  3 tests failed: sanity-hsm, sanityn, sanity.",
